msgstr "# triton.language.umulhi"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:4
msgid "简介：计算x和y的2N位乘积中每个元素的最显著N位。"
msgstr "Introduction: Compute the most significant N bits of each element in the 2N-bit product of x and y."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.umulhi(x, y, _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `x`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `y`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用           |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type     | Description                                      |\n"
"|---------------|----------|--------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| `x`           | `tensor` | Tensor data                                      |\n"
"| `y`           | `tensor` | Tensor data                                      |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -        | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`x`：输出张量的shape与输入x的shape相同\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`x`: The shape of the output tensor is the same as that of the input `x`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 OP 规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:20
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | ×    | ×     | √     | ×     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ×    | ×     | √     | ×     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×     | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | ×    | ×     | √     | ×     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ×    | ×     | √     | ×     | ×     | ×      | ×      | ×     | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    | ×    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:22
msgid ""
"结论：Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 int64 支持。\n"
"torch_npu 对 uint8 的支持。\n"
msgstr ""
"Conclusion: Ascend lacks int64 support compared to GPU.  \n"
"torch_npu supports uint8.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:26
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:28
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both supporting tensors from 1 to 5 dimensions."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:30
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:32
msgid "int64不支持"
msgstr "int64 is not supported"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:34
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:36
msgid "以下示例实现了对输入张量 `x` 做显著N位："
msgstr "The following example implements significant N-bit quantization on the input tensor `x`."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/umulhi.md:38
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def umulhi_kernel(X, Y, Z, N: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    offs = tl.arange(0, N)\n"
"    x = tl.load(X + offs)\n"
"    y = tl.load(Y + offs)\n"
"    z = tl.umulhi(x, y)\n"
"    tl.store(Z + tl.arange(0, N), z)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

